prism

Class ModelVariablesDD

  • java.lang.Object
    • prism.ModelVariablesDD

  • public class ModelVariablesDD
extends java.lang.Object
    Management and information storage about the DD variables used by a symbolic model.
    After use, the variable references should be cleared by calling clear().
